    {
      "chinese": "捕魚的方法有數十種，大都僅能在自家漁區捕魚。其中毒魚法因涉及上下漁區的問題，一般會採集體捕魚方式進行，時間落在豐年祭前夕，以魚藤作為麻痺漁類的藥劑，先在上游敲擊魚藤，再到下游捕獲魚隻，魚獲以均分的方式與部落共享。",
      "ab": "sathaethaimade ka mangesale moabale na saakakay. makasi amanimani kimade ’ikay ko drakealimade ka thakada’ane thoaethae.\r\n tadrapolomyani ka watovadrele, bwalane talebeane ko pidrakealane, nikwani no droapolini ka lakaesale ka sakabaane takapaa, pa’ikay no tatilegese myani, syakay na drapolo patigamee ko kaka’ange, pa’ikay bwalane tokotoko na drapolo, lawa awdro toka’ange, ko alrani kaka’ange ka la lapii ka sakabaane maesale.",
